<h3>How to delete from first space to end of line</h3>

```vim
%s/[ ]\{-1,}..*// or %s/ \{-1,}..*// #non-greedy
%s/[ ]..*// or %s/ ..*//
```

<hr>
<h3>Reduce all multiple white spaces to one space except for leading white space</h3>

```vim
%s/[^ ]\zs  \+/ /g
```